* The vinyl was released in standard black with limited versions in white (US) and blue (UK).
* Four tracks from ''Belong'' were remixed for [[Record Store Day]]. The ''Acid Reflex'' EP was announced, and streamable, on February 24, 2012. <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thisisfakediy.co.uk/articles/news/the-pains-of-being-pure-at-heart-release-record-store-day-ep/# |title=The Pains of Being Pure at Heart Talk Release Record Store Day EP |publisher=This is Fake DIY |date= |accessdate=2011-03-25}}</ref>

